ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c41747a9b4cbd06d2cc4318defc6c2f78985e14e","tid":1488463,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:39:29.000Z","msg":"推 824觀塘見"},{"pid":"c9376f7ecc74b2ef253ca876e04d5d097ebc034d","tid":1488463,"uid":200016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ec8bd5d5dcb7668f5bea18e4c00ba076e5d4e4f5","tid":1488463,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"唔好講推 將今日核彈列明黎推post<br />\n<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 無啦啦拘捕個女人<br />\n5. 室內開槍<br />\n6. 過份使用武力+催淚彈<br />\n7. 冇委任證<br />\n8. 過期催淚彈<br />\n9. 警黑勾結<br />\n10. 無差別濫捕<br />\n11. 光明正大講大話<br />\n12. 誣蔑市民+陷害市民<br />\n13. 拆證物<br />\n14. 無視任何法律及指引<br />\n15. 葉虎事件<br />\n<br />\n佢地搞到香港咁樣 人人都生意差冇工開佢地仲計ot幾萬蚊準時出糧一定唔驚，諗計斷班撚樣既飯碗<br />\n香港人唔再需要唔保護市民既警察！！唔想再出糧俾一啲開槍打我 用棍扑我既人"},{"pid":"6d52bcc39b42cdc582116a7ffa5d1ca03d8bb5e0","tid":1488463,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:50:14.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"87d195eba0c1b04fed9844ed2e7fa0b2716055c6","tid":1488463,"uid":200016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vH8WFUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvH8WFUK.png&h=413623cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39b8238e3274210192d2f73b7b134269de7260fd","tid":1488463,"uid":200016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eC7HBs9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeC7HBs9.png&h=e5c3e71d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p